1
00:00:00,310 --> 00:00:01,710
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,080
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,350 --> 00:00:08,350
Sir,

5
00:00:09,510 --> 00:00:10,520
there's...

6
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:13,620
something I haven't told you yet.

7
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:15,450
It's about Hyun Jun.

8
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:18,890
You...

9
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:23,130
What are you about to say?

10
00:00:33,510 --> 00:00:36,210
You'd better watch your mouth.

11
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:39,010
If you mess with my Hyun Jun,
I'll kill you.

12
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:44,250
Sir,

13
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,650
Hyun Jun...

14
00:00:50,190 --> 00:00:52,320
married Chloe today.

15
00:00:55,830 --> 00:00:58,830
What? He got married?

16
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:00,900
You...

17
00:01:01,370 --> 00:01:03,870
This wedding went ahead
without your permission.

18
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:07,110
You need to decide
what you're going to do about it.

19
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:22,090
While I was collapsed and dying,

20
00:01:22,850 --> 00:01:24,290
you had a wedding?

21
00:01:24,820 --> 00:01:26,160
After leaving me incapacitated...

22
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,890
and causing chaos
throughout the company,

23
00:01:28,290 --> 00:01:30,860
you even threw a celebration
on top of that?

24
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,300
I'd expect that from Oh Jung Ran,

25
00:01:34,970 --> 00:01:37,700
but my own son betraying me?

26
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,570
It's a marriage
you already approved of.

27
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,970
For the joint venture
on the exclusive development rights,

28
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,710
it was absolutely necessary.

29
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:47,310
Please try to understand Hyun Jun.

30
00:01:50,380 --> 00:01:54,020
Hyun Jun did nothing wrong.

31
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:56,050
He didn't want to, but I insisted.

32
00:01:56,050 --> 00:01:58,360
Yes, everything...

33
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:02,060
is on you, Oh Jung Ran.

34
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:05,160
Right then and there,
I should have...

35
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,470
finished you off for good.

36
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:17,380
Finished her off? What do you mean?

37
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:22,550
- Wait. Did you try to kill Mom?
- That's right!

38
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:26,850
That thing stabbed me in the back
and tried to kill my son.

39
00:02:27,650 --> 00:02:30,390
She had to be dealt with for good.

40
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,190
How could you...

41
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,960
How could you do that to Mom?

42
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,060
Calm down, okay?

43
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:45,540
Is killing me
all you can think about even now?

44
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:51,540
Fine. I was a fool
to waste time scheming.

45
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:54,180
I should've just finished you
when I had the chance.

46
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,180
Oh Jung Ran!

47
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:59,020
Don't get too comfortable.

48
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,320
You think Kim Myung Hui saved you?

49
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:03,920
No.

50
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:07,830
Believe me when I say
she'll betray you,

51
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:09,630
just like she did to me.

52
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:11,160
Shut it!

53
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,970
How dare you raise your voice at me?

54
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:17,970
How dare you
put me out of commission...

55
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:20,270
and then yell at me?

56
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,640
Kim Myung Hui!

57
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:26,240
Drag all of them out of here now
and kill them all.

58
00:03:27,050 --> 00:03:28,710
Sir!

59
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:31,050
Get the chairman inside. Quickly.

60
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,550
Oh Jung Ran.

61
00:03:32,950 --> 00:03:34,590
Lock her in the basement
immediately.

62
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:37,660
Make sure she never sees
the light of day again.

63
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:42,830
Let go of me. You...
Park Tae Ho, Kim Myung Hui.

64
00:03:43,090 --> 00:03:44,900
I'll make you pay for this!

65
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,670
- Mom.
- Stop right there.

66
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,070
You brat.

67
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,770
If you want to remain in this house
as my son,

68
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:56,810
cut ties with your mother.

69
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:01,650
Otherwise, you can follow
your mother to the basement.

70
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:02,680
Father!

71
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,520
Hyun Jun.

72
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,690
Let go of me.

73
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:12,490
Hey.

74
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,130
Hey, open the door.

75
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,330
Open this door right now!

76
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,950
How could he do that to my mom?

77
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:43,320
And I had no idea.

78
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,530
Do you think my father
will let her live?

79
00:04:49,690 --> 00:04:51,560
If anything happens to her...

80
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,030
We know where he put her,

81
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,630
and so does President Kim.

82
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:57,700
Chairman Park won't dare
to make a move.

83
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:04,610
My family just keeps getting worse.

84
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:09,680
My father is trying
to kill my mother, so she...

85
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,580
But then President Kim went
and woke him up.

86
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:20,190
Should we just leave everything behind
and run away?

87
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:23,460
- If we could get out of here...
- We can't run away.

88
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,470
Right.

89
00:05:29,170 --> 00:05:31,470
I mean, you have a job to do.

90
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,670
That's the whole reason
we got married.

91
00:05:36,910 --> 00:05:38,010
I'm sorry, I...

92
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:41,380
I hate that I sound so weak
on our first day of marriage.

93
00:05:47,350 --> 00:05:48,350
For now,

94
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,390
it's best
not to provoke Chairman Park.

95
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,590
Even if you're worried
about your mother,

96
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:55,730
please be patient.

97
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,930
As for how to handle this...

98
00:05:58,660 --> 00:05:59,960
I'll find a way.

99
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,970
I want to help you.

100
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,650
I want to get you
right where you want to be.

101
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:23,020
Our marriage still stands, right?

102
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:26,220
You're not going to end our marriage
just because my father...

103
00:06:28,890 --> 00:06:31,430
didn't approve of me
becoming chairman, are you?

104
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:33,460
It's not over yet.

105
00:06:34,970 --> 00:06:36,000
Somehow,

106
00:06:36,770 --> 00:06:38,400
we're going to see our plan through.

107
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:41,570
Okay. I get it.

108
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:44,180
That's all I need to hear.

109
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,580
I made a mistake.

110
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:29,950
I should've taken you out
along with Park Tae Ho.

111
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,620
I should've killed Park Tae Ho...

112
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:35,630
and gotten rid of you
and Park Min Jun too.

113
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:38,560
Trying to buy time
for Hyun Jun's sake...

114
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:39,630
was my mistake.

115
00:07:42,330 --> 00:07:44,840
Still acting all smug, are you?

116
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:46,770
That attitude could get you killed.

117
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:49,740
What did you say?

118
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:53,780
Chairman Park told me to handle you
as I see fit.

119
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:58,150
He probably wants
to kill you right now.

120
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,150
If I don't stop him,

121
00:08:02,650 --> 00:08:05,490
you could really die here.

122
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,360
What?

123
00:08:08,690 --> 00:08:11,760
And of course, your son's life...

124
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,100
is still in my hands.

125
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,200
You saw what happened just now.

126
00:08:16,730 --> 00:08:19,800
I almost revealed Hyun Jun's secret.

127
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:23,940
Why are you doing this to me?

128
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:27,780
I offered you half of Adele Group.
Wasn't that enough?

129
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:29,580
Are you trying to take over
all of Adele?

130
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,620
Half of Adele Group?

131
00:08:35,650 --> 00:08:37,590
From the very beginning,
my target...

132
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:39,390
was you,

133
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:41,490
Oh Jung Ran.

134
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,360
What?

135
00:08:43,730 --> 00:08:47,830
For the last 30 years, I've had
only one thought while watching you.

136
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:50,370
How...

137
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,470
can I make you pay for what you did?

138
00:08:58,110 --> 00:09:02,580
Myung Hui, don't go.
Please, don't go!

139
00:09:02,650 --> 00:09:06,280
- Let her go in peace.
- No! How can I let her go?

140
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,020
Myung Hui!

141
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:10,120
Oh no, Min Jun!

142
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:14,960
Min Jun!
Oh no. This can't be happening.

143
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:20,400
How could I make you feel
the same sadness and pain I felt?

144
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:24,100
What's the right punishment
for a murderer like Oh Jung Ran?

145
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:25,270
A murderer?

146
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,940
What, that incident at Munhwadang?

147
00:09:28,570 --> 00:09:31,010
Why do you want revenge
when it had nothing to do with you?

148
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,980
You and Park Min Jun
are both alive and well,

149
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,950
so what sadness and pain
are you even talking about?

150
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,550
Right.

151
00:09:37,850 --> 00:09:41,350
I didn't expect you to feel
any remorse or regret.

152
00:09:43,290 --> 00:09:44,860
Anyway, now...

153
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:50,430
you'll feel the pain and fear
of losing what you hold dear.

154
00:09:55,370 --> 00:09:57,030
What's this?

155
00:09:58,540 --> 00:10:01,240
No, let go of me. Let go.

156
00:10:01,610 --> 00:10:02,610
Darn you!

157
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,140
(Applicant: Oh Jung Ran)

158
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:09,880
Are you crazy?

159
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:14,390
And it all starts...

160
00:10:14,690 --> 00:10:17,290
with you losing your position
at Adele Group.

161
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:19,860
No way. Says who?

162
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:25,300
You think some stupid piece of paper
is going to end all this?

163
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:28,270
After everything I did to become
the lady of the Adele Group,

164
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:30,370
I'm not letting it end like this.

165
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:33,770
Do you remember what I said
the day you were kicked out?

166
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:37,140
I'm holding your son's life hostage,

167
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:39,980
and all you can do is
sit back and take it.

168
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:44,650
Now that I have your life
in my hands as well,

169
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,520
you'd better be very careful.

170
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:50,450
Next time, you'll lose things
far more precious than this,

171
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,120
and the pain...

172
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:56,530
will be unbearable.

173
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:02,930
Wait. Hold on.
What do you think you're doing?

174
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,800
No, wait.

175
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,440
What the...

176
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,610
Jung Ran.

177
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:11,310
I'll at least...

178
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,050
let the two of you stay together.

179
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:23,650
Ms. Kim, wait. Ms. Kim!

180
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,890
Jung Ran.

181
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:32,460
Kim Myung Hui...

182
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:54,120
What's going on? Why are you here?

183
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:57,960
Your mother woke up Chairman Park.

184
00:12:01,460 --> 00:12:04,560
So he's finally awake.

185
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,430
I take it...

186
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:11,400
you knew about the plan
to wake Chairman Park?

187
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:15,340
Go on in.

188
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:19,940
Your mother's acting like
she owns Adele.

189
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:48,970
Your marriage.

190
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:51,040
It wasn't for love, was it?

191
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,480
You said it was for your revenge.

192
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:55,850
What are you trying to achieve
with this marriage?

193
00:12:55,850 --> 00:12:58,220
Why do you want to be
a part of the Adele family?

194
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:00,380
Don't tell me...

195
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:03,450
Are you trying to steal Adele
from my father?

196
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,960
Yes.

197
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,390
If I can't take
Chairman Park's life,

198
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:14,600
then I'll take Adele, the one thing
he cherishes like life itself.

199
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:18,570
Then you should've chosen me,
not Hyun Jun.

200
00:13:20,170 --> 00:13:21,410
I did.

201
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:26,040
But then you almost died.

202
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:35,690
I...

203
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,390
had to watch...

204
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:44,530
my dad die
right in front of my eyes.

205
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:48,470
And then you, just like him,

206
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,740
ended up a bloody mess
right in front of me.

207
00:13:56,440 --> 00:14:00,680
You barely survived
and didn't remember anything.

208
00:14:03,110 --> 00:14:04,780
What was I supposed to do?

209
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:11,020
But I remember everything now.

210
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:13,520
If you want Adele,

211
00:14:14,530 --> 00:14:15,860
let me help you.

212
00:14:18,230 --> 00:14:19,230
No.

213
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:23,830
You don't help me get revenge.

214
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:26,200
You just get in the way.

215
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,470
Just look.

216
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:31,780
Today, you tried to ruin my wedding,
and your mother...

217
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:37,280
ruined my plan
by waking up Chairman Park.

218
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:39,480
On top of that, your mother...

219
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:44,050
is the person protecting
Chairman Park for Adele's sake.

220
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:50,160
Could you really go against
your own father and mother...

221
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:52,960
just for me?

222
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,570
Jin Ju, that's...

223
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:03,940
Please.

224
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:06,080
Min Jun.

225
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:09,280
Please.

226
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,080
Just let me go.

227
00:15:14,350 --> 00:15:15,390
Please.

228
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:19,560
Min Jun, please.

229
00:15:22,530 --> 00:15:23,730
I'm begging you.

230
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:48,450
(Seoul Family Court)

231
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:52,020
I've locked Oh Jung Ran
in the annex's basement,

232
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:54,120
and I've obtained her signature
on the divorce papers.

233
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,930
With your permission, sir,

234
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:58,200
I'll file them immediately.

235
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:03,200
Good. Stamp them with my seal...

236
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,340
and hand them over
to the lawyer right away.

237
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:09,840
As for Oh Jung Ran,
once the divorce is finalized,

238
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:11,840
I'll deal with her immediately.

239
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:15,550
What do you mean by that?

240
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:19,380
Are you really going to kill her?

241
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,020
Don't tell me...

242
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:23,920
you've forgiven Oh Jung Ran.

243
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,090
Of course not.

244
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:27,520
How could I ever forgive her?

245
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,160
I just...

246
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:32,400
don't want to have...

247
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:35,030
blood on my hands like she does.

248
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:37,300
Once you have blood on your hands,

249
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:39,140
the price of that sin...

250
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,310
is always...

251
00:16:42,110 --> 00:16:43,570
paid in blood.

252
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:50,380
By the way, where's Min Jun?

253
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:53,580
What happened? Why isn't he here?

254
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:58,120
There was a lot to be done
to wake you up, sir.

255
00:16:58,620 --> 00:17:01,390
He's finishing up with the antidote
and the security detail.

256
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:04,230
He'll come greet you when he's done.

257
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:07,300
Of course.

258
00:17:07,930 --> 00:17:09,070
A son of mine...

259
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:13,370
should've done everything he could
to wake me up.

260
00:17:21,850 --> 00:17:22,850
Sir.

261
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:28,920
Right, of course.

262
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:31,690
I almost forgot about him.
Manager Kang.

263
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:34,830
I've heard all about what you did.

264
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:38,860
You sided with Oh Jung Ran...

265
00:17:39,260 --> 00:17:42,770
to forge a power of attorney
and falsify medical records?

266
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:45,970
I'm sorry, sir. I have no excuse.

267
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:50,770
Manager Kang was blackmailed.
He had no other choice.

268
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:58,120
He said that when you woke up,
he wanted to return to his post.

269
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:00,680
Please forgive him.

270
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:02,050
That's true.

271
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:04,090
Please forgive me, sir.

272
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:05,560
Is that so?

273
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:09,560
Myung Hui, I'll trust your judgment.

274
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:12,560
I'm giving you one more chance,

275
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:15,030
so you'd better
get your act together.

276
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:16,300
Thank you.

277
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:18,040
Thank you, sir.

278
00:18:18,570 --> 00:18:21,570
I'll be stopping by the office
tomorrow, so be prepared.

279
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:23,640
Already?

280
00:18:23,910 --> 00:18:25,480
You should rest more.

281
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,010
No, I'm fine.

282
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:29,110
I made the decision
after consulting my doctor.

283
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:34,450
- Get everything ready.
- Yes, sir. Understood.

284
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:52,800
Thank you.

285
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:56,210
I'm in your debt, Ms. Kim.

286
00:18:56,510 --> 00:19:00,180
Yes, and you'll have
to repay me one day.

287
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:02,510
Of course. I promise you that.

288
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:05,620
For now, since the chairman
will be coming to the office,

289
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,750
get everything ready.

290
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:08,920
Revoke Oh Jung Ran's
power of attorney...

291
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,890
and proceed with the divorce.

292
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:12,820
Yes, ma'am.

293
00:19:14,860 --> 00:19:15,860
Secretary Jung.

294
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:18,260
Ask Butler Ok to come back.

295
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:19,960
Yes, ma'am.

296
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:23,200
I'll be on my way then.

297
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:35,750
- Min Jun.
- Sir.

298
00:19:36,080 --> 00:19:38,320
What happened?
We couldn't get ahold of you.

299
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:43,020
Your father woke up. Go say hello.

300
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:47,420
Are you really that happy?

301
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,960
I didn't even remember
what kind of man my father was,

302
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,830
and you stood by...

303
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:55,530
while I humiliated myself
trying to save him.

304
00:19:55,530 --> 00:19:58,200
Are you happy now
that you insisted on waking him up?

305
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:00,100
Sir.

306
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:02,870
Are your memories back?

307
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:10,150
We need to talk.

308
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:23,130
Where have you been?

309
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:26,630
Did you have any headaches?
Did you go to the hospital?

310
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:29,700
You still...

311
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:33,340
think I deceived you, don't you?

312
00:20:36,610 --> 00:20:38,980
That's right. For your sake.

313
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:42,480
I decided it was best for you
to forget those painful memories,

314
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:45,520
but maybe that was selfish of me.

315
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:48,450
I'm sorry.

316
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:52,920
I know...

317
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,860
my accident was hard on you,

318
00:20:57,290 --> 00:20:58,930
so I've tried to be understanding.

319
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,800
But when I think about all the time
I spent without my memory,

320
00:21:04,230 --> 00:21:06,200
I honestly resent you for it.

321
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:09,440
I don't think I can face Father...

322
00:21:10,770 --> 00:21:13,180
the same way I did
when I had amnesia.

323
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,880
As for Father,

324
00:21:18,980 --> 00:21:20,250
I'll see him later.

325
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:21,520
Min Jun.

326
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,760
What if...

327
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:38,870
I decided to give up on Adele Group
and hand it over to someone else?

328
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:40,570
What would you do?

329
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:43,670
What do you mean by that?

330
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:45,540
I'm...

331
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,980
just wondering, hypothetically.

332
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:52,420
You're the owner
of Adele Group, Min Jun.

333
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:55,550
No one can ever take your place.

334
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:01,260
I'll head upstairs.

335
00:22:14,170 --> 00:22:16,540
Did Min Jun really get
his memory back?

336
00:22:17,170 --> 00:22:19,310
When? How?

337
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:29,120
I can't believe
Chairman Park woke up.

338
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:31,460
I suspected as much.

339
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:33,160
President Kim Myung Hui...

340
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:36,930
deliberately provoked Oh Jung Ran
into rushing the wedding.

341
00:22:37,390 --> 00:22:40,830
It was a diversion
so she could wake up Chairman Park.

342
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,130
I should've known something was off.

343
00:22:45,970 --> 00:22:47,670
After all the trouble
to get married...

344
00:22:47,870 --> 00:22:48,970
Unbelievable.

345
00:22:50,170 --> 00:22:53,080
Now that she's woken him up,
things have changed.

346
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,380
At this rate,

347
00:22:56,410 --> 00:22:58,850
Park Min Jun will become
the successor.

348
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:06,020
Even now, our best bet is
to join forces with him...

349
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:07,960
and take down Chairman Park.

350
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:11,330
- I'm married to Park Hyun Jun.
- But...

351
00:23:11,330 --> 00:23:15,530
Besides, this whole incident
has shown me what kind of person...

352
00:23:15,970 --> 00:23:17,530
President Kim really is.

353
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:22,270
She wants Adele so much
that getting half of it...

354
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:24,240
wouldn't satisfy her.

355
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:28,040
She's protecting Chairman Park
for the sake of Adele.

356
00:23:29,710 --> 00:23:32,050
To take down Chairman Park
and take over Adele,

357
00:23:32,120 --> 00:23:34,250
we'd have to fight her.

358
00:23:35,090 --> 00:23:37,750
And Park Min Jun can't fight
his mother.

359
00:23:39,490 --> 00:23:41,690
If I want to save
my marriage with Hyun Jun...

360
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:43,560
and be accepted by the Adele family,

361
00:23:44,230 --> 00:23:47,660
I need to prepare
to go up against President Kim.

362
00:23:55,170 --> 00:23:58,510
I think Min Jun was deeply hurt
by Chloe.

363
00:23:59,140 --> 00:24:01,510
He seemed ready to give up
on his goal...

364
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:02,950
of taking over Adele Group.

365
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:05,850
It hasn't even been a full day
since he got his memory back,

366
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:07,320
and so much has happened.

367
00:24:07,320 --> 00:24:08,920
But isn't it strange?

368
00:24:10,390 --> 00:24:15,060
Min Jun is trying to give up
on taking over Adele Group...

369
00:24:15,130 --> 00:24:18,730
while Hyun Jun is becoming
more obsessed with it.

370
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,770
Chloe supposedly lost her memory,

371
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,730
yet she got married...

372
00:24:25,140 --> 00:24:27,140
and wants to become
part of the Adele family.

373
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:31,210
Now that you mention it,
that is strange.

374
00:24:32,080 --> 00:24:35,110
What if Chloe never lost her memory?

375
00:24:35,580 --> 00:24:36,580
What?

376
00:24:38,450 --> 00:24:42,120
Is that why she's still so fixated
on Adele Group?

377
00:24:42,250 --> 00:24:43,690
What if getting married...

378
00:24:43,950 --> 00:24:45,960
was part of her plan
to take over all of Adele Group,

379
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:47,960
not just the bio division?

380
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:55,930
- Sir.
- Goodness.

381
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:58,600
Sir, are you all right?

382
00:24:58,800 --> 00:25:00,140
I trust you've all been well?

383
00:25:00,370 --> 00:25:02,370
Did something happen to you?

384
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,980
You little... That's right.

385
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:09,880
Hey, there. Park Min Jun!

386
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:13,950
Right.

387
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:20,490
I know it wasn't easy,
but you did a great job,

388
00:25:22,130 --> 00:25:24,030
unlike a certain someone.

389
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,760
Not at all, sir.

390
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,530
And humble too.

391
00:25:30,730 --> 00:25:34,640
That's my son, the heir to Adele.

392
00:25:36,740 --> 00:25:39,740
I'll be making
the official announcement soon,

393
00:25:39,810 --> 00:25:41,180
so be ready.

394
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:45,380
I'll do it
after I catch up on company work.

395
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:48,320
- Let's go.
- Yes, sir.

396
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:05,740
(Head of Division 1, Park Min Jun)

397
00:26:13,610 --> 00:26:14,680
Min Jun.

398
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:21,690
Why are you really here?

399
00:26:22,090 --> 00:26:24,220
Are you here to apologize...

400
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:27,060
- or to make excuses?
- I...

401
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:35,230
I wasn't trying to deceive you.
I just wanted to help.

402
00:26:36,370 --> 00:26:37,930
You remember everything now.

403
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,600
Think back
to when you'd lost your memory.

404
00:26:40,670 --> 00:26:43,010
When you had headaches,

405
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:45,310
you said holding my hand
made you feel better.

406
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:47,180
You were the one...

407
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:49,450
who looked at me so warmly
and smiled first.

408
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:53,480
All I did was give you what you wanted
and help you.

409
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:56,190
So, excuses it is.

410
00:26:57,650 --> 00:27:01,060
Just like you stole Jin Ju's design
and took over her life,

411
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:06,130
you pretended to be her
to deceive and use me.

412
00:27:06,530 --> 00:27:08,100
Yet, here you are making excuses
instead of apologizing.

413
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,100
I...

414
00:27:10,130 --> 00:27:12,370
went as far as imitating Jin Ju...

415
00:27:12,870 --> 00:27:14,540
just to be there for you.

416
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:18,640
Your mother gave me permission,
saying it was all for you.

417
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:22,880
Right.
Both you and my mother deceived me.

418
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:27,250
If you really wanted to help,
you should've been honest with me...

419
00:27:27,250 --> 00:27:29,190
and helped me get my memory back.

420
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:31,020
If you'd done that,

421
00:27:31,490 --> 00:27:33,090
I would've seen you differently.

422
00:27:33,090 --> 00:27:34,460
I would've been grateful,

423
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:37,960
and I wouldn't loathe you
the way I do now.

424
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,960
What?

425
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,970
I disgust you?

426
00:27:44,130 --> 00:27:45,140
You loathe me?

427
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:49,910
I could say much worse,
so just get out.

428
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:58,680
(Head of Division 1, Park Min Jun)

429
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:07,090
He's disgusted with me?

430
00:28:08,730 --> 00:28:10,090
He loathes me?

431
00:28:19,900 --> 00:28:21,770
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

432
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:24,140
Sir, you asked to see me?

433
00:28:24,210 --> 00:28:28,710
Right. There's something
I wanted to give you myself.

434
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:33,880
What's this?

435
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:36,020
Open it.

436
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,790
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

437
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:39,960
(Board of Directors Resolution)

438
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:41,490
(Letter of Appointment
as Acting Chairman)

439
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:46,230
Sir.

440
00:28:47,430 --> 00:28:50,330
This will be approved
at the next board meeting.

441
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,000
While I recover,

442
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:55,110
I want you to take that seat.

443
00:28:56,570 --> 00:28:59,040
You'll receive
all kinds of information...

444
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:01,580
and reports about the group,
so handle them.

445
00:29:02,250 --> 00:29:04,550
You also need to make Min Jun...

446
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:06,320
the official successor.

447
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:11,220
The only people I can trust now
are you, Myung Hui...

448
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:14,120
and Min Jun.

449
00:29:15,490 --> 00:29:16,860
Thank you, sir.

450
00:29:17,090 --> 00:29:18,290
There's no need to thank me.

451
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:21,100
You saved my life.

452
00:29:23,930 --> 00:29:24,930
Go ahead.

453
00:29:26,840 --> 00:29:27,970
Give that seat a try.

454
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:37,880
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

455
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:53,730
Sir, I have something urgent
to report.

456
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:57,530
- What is it?
- It's about Temi Bio.

457
00:29:59,170 --> 00:30:00,240
Temi Bio?

458
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:12,220
Why are you looking all serious?

459
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:15,120
Why did you call us here?

460
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,090
Manager Kang.

461
00:30:19,390 --> 00:30:20,390
Yes, sir.

462
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:31,730
You punk!

463
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,540
Sir!

464
00:30:37,570 --> 00:30:39,740
You had the nerve to make
a documentary exposing me...

465
00:30:41,210 --> 00:30:43,380
while I was unconscious
and out of commission?

466
00:30:44,650 --> 00:30:47,120
You pulled a stunt like that
just to remove me...

467
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,020
as chairman?

468
00:30:53,260 --> 00:30:54,290
Park Hyun Jun.

469
00:30:55,730 --> 00:30:57,960
You're no longer my son.

470
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:01,500
- Father!
- Sir.

471
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:12,510
And you.

472
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:15,480
You used the exclusive development rights
to distract me,

473
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,680
so you could betray me?

474
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:21,220
No matter how I look at it,
you never lost your memory.

475
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:23,820
You pretended to have amnesia,

476
00:31:24,650 --> 00:31:27,520
and you're still after Adele.

477
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,560
Are you still suspicious of me?

478
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,760
What will it take
for you to believe me?

479
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:32,800
Quiet!

480
00:31:33,230 --> 00:31:34,700
You can't fool me.

481
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,770
Tell me the truth!

482
00:31:37,370 --> 00:31:38,840
- Stop it!
- Don't!

483
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:44,040
She's my wife now.

484
00:31:45,580 --> 00:31:46,740
Don't you dare touch her.

485
00:31:47,610 --> 00:31:49,250
Exactly. That's enough.

486
00:31:49,810 --> 00:31:53,380
I was the one who commissioned
the Temi Bio documentary.

487
00:31:59,490 --> 00:32:01,420
- What?
- Min Jun.

488
00:32:07,430 --> 00:32:08,530
I get why he'd do it,

489
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:11,530
since he couldn't care less
whether I lived or died.

490
00:32:13,370 --> 00:32:14,370
But you?

491
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:17,310
You saved me,
so why would you do that?

492
00:32:51,570 --> 00:32:54,510
(Pearl in Red)

493
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:57,550
So they're really going to dig up
that incident from seven years ago?

494
00:32:57,610 --> 00:33:00,120
What do I do?
If they find out what I did,

495
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,480
it'll all be over for good.

496
00:33:01,850 --> 00:33:05,150
You may think you helped us,
but you didn't.

497
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:07,160
If you ask me,
you just made things worse.

498
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,220
Thanks to you,

499
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:10,630
now I have to deal
with both Father and your mother.

500
00:33:10,630 --> 00:33:12,730
Yu Na. What's this?

501
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:14,030
(Suicide Note)

502
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,800
A suicide note?

503
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,600
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
